{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779169238169,"sessionID":"ses_1c140741affedi5WfnaXcYFn6q","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"webfetch","callID":"call_02_gXhTZadgObDwl04N77yv8916","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"url":"https://www.zumper.com/","format":"markdown","timeout":30},"output":"Zumper - Houses, Condos, and Apartments for Rent                     \n\n[![Zumper](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/zumperDarkText.664a5ef8.svg)](/)\n\n[Advertise](https://advertise.zumper.com/)[Manage rentals](/manage)[Marketing Studio](/manage/portal)\n\n## Find your fresh start\n\n# Discover millions of houses and apartments for rent.\n\n![](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/search.272ccae9.svg)\n\n![Location](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/locationAutocomplete.81057160.svg)\n\nUse your current location\n\nPopular\n\n![](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/Zipcode.08d98c96.svg)\n\nNew York, NY\n\n![](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/Zipcode.08d98c96.svg)\n\nSan Francisco, CA\n\n![](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/Zipcode.08d98c96.svg)\n\nChicago, IL\n\n![](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/Zipcode.08d98c96.svg)\n\nVancouver, BC\n\n![](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/Zipcode.08d98c96.svg)\n\nToronto, ON\n\n![](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/Zipcode.08d98c96.svg)\n\nMontréal, QC\n\n## Renting made easy\n\nHelping millions of renters navigate the rental market with confidence.\n\n![](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/comprehensiveListings.d279ced0.svg)\n\n### Comprehensive listings\n\nBrowse and apply to over 1 million listings with long or short term leases throughout the U.S. and Canada.\n\n![](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/usefulResources.d2e569af.svg)\n\n### Useful resources\n\nMake informed decisions with our rent trends, city guides, affordability calculator, and Zumper Expert Ratings.\n\n![](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/peaceOfMind.cfc8536a.svg)\n\n### Peace of mind\n\nFeel secure on your rental journey, knowing we're committed to accuracy and providing verified listings.\n\nOne sec, gathering the spotlight listings\n\nOne sec, gathering the nearby listings\n\nOne sec, gathering the popular cities\n\nOne sec, gathering the about the app\n\nOne sec, gathering the Zumper National Rent Report\n\nOne sec, gathering the marketing section\n\nOne sec, gathering the press section\n\nOne sec, gathering the FAQ section\n\nOne sec, gathering the homepage links\n\n### ![zumper](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/zumper_logo.91f43aea.svg)\n\nFind your fresh start™.\n\n© 2026 Zumper Inc.\n\n[![Zumper on Facebook](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/fb_icon.542703d3.svg)](https://facebook.com/zumperinc)[![Zumper on Twitter](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/twitter_icon.e2965285.svg)](https://twitter.com/zumper)[![Zumper on Instagram](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/insta_icon.f1e23da9.svg)](https://instagram.com/zumper)[![Zumper on Pinterest](https://d214hhm15p4t1d.cloudfront.net/web-zumper/8e31343b8c5136357a3f6c9b9ae0df91c7446258/img/pin_icon.74893c7b.svg)](https://pinterest.com/zumper/)\n