{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779169258952,"sessionID":"ses_1c140741affedi5WfnaXcYFn6q","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"webfetch","callID":"call_01_dHcCYlOKWH3ioFX8h1gW7773","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"format":"markdown","timeout":30,"url":"https://www.rent.com/"},"output":"Rent. Find your next place | Apartments and Houses for Rent. \n\n  \n\nSkip to Content (Press Enter)[](/)\n\n-   [0](/saved)\n-   [List a Property](/list)\n-   [Business Solutions](/solutions)\n-   [Moving Center](https://www.rent.com/blog/moving-center/)\n-   Log In\n-   Sign Up\n\n# Find your  \nperfect place.\n\nThese properties are trending in your area. Find hot deals, tour a property or contact an agent.\n\n## Renter tips and insights\n\nAdvice from our experts to help you along your rental journey.\n\n[Visit Rent Blog](https://www.rent.com/blog)\n\n[\n\n![](/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fwoman-writing-in-journal.2617551c.png&w=3840&q=75)\n\n11 Steps to Follow When Renting an Apartment\n\nApartment hunting can be exciting, yet overwhelming. Simplify the task by getting organized.\n\n\n\n](https://www.rent.com/blog/how-to-rent-an-apartment/)[\n\n![](/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fcalculator.60a6a113.png&w=3840&q=75)\n\nRent Calculator: How Much Should You Spend on Rent?\n\nLet us know your income, expenses and desired location. We'll help you find the right rent budget.\n\n\n\n](https://www.rent.com/blog/rent-calculator/)[\n\n![](/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fman-on-computer.5e9a8f03.png&w=3840&q=75)\n\nThe Best US Cities for Hybrid Work\n\nSee where America's hybrid workers are living and thriving.\n\n\n\n](https://www.rent.com/blog/the-best-cities-for-hybrid-work/)\n\n[](/ \"Rent.\")\n\n-   [](https://www.facebook.com/rent \"Facebook\")\n-   [](https://twitter.com/rentdotcom \"Twitter\")\n-   [](https://www.tiktok.com/@rent.tok \"Tiktok\")\n-   [](https://www.pinterest.com/rentdotcom/ \"Pinterest\")\n-   [](https://www.youtube.com/rentdotcom \"YouTube\")\n-   [](https://instagram.com/rent.social \"Instagram\")\n\nOur Company\n\n-   [Redfin.com](https://www.redfin.com)\n-   [Rent Blog](https://www.rent.com/blog/)\n-   [Rent Research](https://www.rent.com/research/)\n-   [Privacy Policy](/legal/privacy-policy)\n-   [Terms of Service](/legal/terms-of-service)\n-   [Do Not Share or Sell My Personal Information](/legal/do-not-sell)\n\nPopular Searches\n\n-   [Apartments for Rent Near Me](/near-me/apartments)\n-   [Houses for Rent Near Me](/near-me/houses)\n-   [1 Bedroom Apartments Near Me](/near-me/1-bedroom-apartments)\n-   [Studio Apartments Near Me](/near-me/studio-apartments)\n-   [Cheap Houses Near Me](/near-me/cheap-houses)\n-   [Luxury Apartments Near Me](/near-me/luxury-apartments)\n-   [Pet Friendly Apartments Near Me](/near-me/pet-friendly-apartments)\n\nLet Us Help\n\n-   [Download App](/mobile-apps)\n-   [Avoid Scams](/company/security/)\n-   [List a Property](/list)\n-   [Business Solutions](/solutions)\n-   [Site Map](/sitemap)\n-   [Accessibility](tel:8447597732)\n-   [Rental Price Estimator](/rent-estimator)\n\nDownload the Rent. app for [Android](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.rent&referrer=ts%3D96e725f6-e305-11e4-9781-00163cabc4e4/) and [iOS](https://apps.apple.com/us/app/rent-com-apartments-home-rentals/id388038507?mt=8/).\n\n© 2026 Rent Group Inc. All rights reserved.\n\n[Terms of Service](/legal/terms-of-service), [Privacy Policy](/legal/privacy-policy) and [MLS Disclosures](/mls-disclosures).\n\nIf you are using a screen reader, or are having difficulty reading this website, please call 1-844-759-7732.\n\n[![Equal Housing Logo](data:image/svg+xml;base64,)](/legal/equal-housing-opportunity \"Equal Housing Opportunity\")\n\nRent Group, operator of Rent., is committed to and abides by the Fair Housing Act and Equal Opportunity Act. Read our [Fair Housing Policy](/legal/equal-housing-opportunity) and [The New York State Fair Housing Notice.](https://dos.ny.gov/sys